{{unreferenced|date=May 2018}} {{Georgians}}
The '''Georgian calendar''' ({{lang-ka|ქართული კალენდარი}}) is the ancient or modern calendar of '''[[Georgia (country)|Georgia]]'''.
Though Georgia now uses the modern [[Gregorian calendar]], the old names for the months are still used.
== Old month names ==
