'''''Late Modernism: Art, Culture, and Politics in Cold War America''''' is a history book about [[late modernism]] as a historical period of aesthetics between modernism and postmodernism. The book was written by Robert Genter and published by [[University of Pennsylvania Press]] in 2010.

