'''Muthurangam Govt. Arts College''' ('''MGAC''') is located in [[Bagayam]], [[Vellore]], [[Tamil Nadu]], India. The college is affiliated with [[Thiruvalluvar University]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Affiliated College of Thiruvalluvar University |url=http://tvu.edu.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Courses_Offered_in_affiliated_colleges.pdf|}}</ref> This college offers different courses in arts, commerce and science.
==History== '''Muthurangam Govt. Arts College''' was inaugurated on 1965 by then Chief Minister Hon'able. Backthavachalam.
